title: 783. Previewing Top Offensive Linemen & Wide Receivers Ahead of Combine
itunes:title: 783. Previewing Top Offensive Linemen & Wide Receivers Ahead of Combine
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys emphasize the importance of the combine. Then, the duo preview the top offensive linemen ahead of the combine. For the rest of the show, the pair touch on the top wide receivers and look back at how they compare to the 2021 wide receiver class.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
